Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.07,0:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一百四十年前\N幕府末年的動亂最盛時期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都有個被稱為\N殺人拔刀齋的志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.11,0:01:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宛如阿修羅般的殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.04,0:01:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開創明治新時代\N最強的男人拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.62,0:01:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是。。他於動亂結束後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失的無影無綜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的行蹤成為一個謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.83,0:02:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人拔刀齋的名字便成為傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.80,0:02:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一話\N傳說中的美劍士\N因愛戰鬥的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治11年\N東京小工商業集中地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.83,0:02:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下    殺人拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於被我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人拔刀齋\N你比我想像的還要斯文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧~~！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.79,0:03:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你真的是\N傳說中的殺人者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.09,0:03:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天晚上\N也於一瞬間殺了三個人嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生是流浪人\N沒有目的地的流浪劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為這個能殺人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼？刀刃相反的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆刃刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.51,0:03:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不能殺人   我也沒有殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這刀刃上確實沒有一個缺口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟新的刀一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的疑慮好像已經消除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.47,0:03:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近每天晚上拔刀齋都會\N出現在街上暗殺行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.27,0:03:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候你帶著刀晃來晃去\N誰都會把你認錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.64,0:04:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這明治的社會中帶刀\N是被法律所禁止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是真的吧？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.27,0:04:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太厲害了！這麼厲害\N難道是傳說中的殺人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齋！到這裏為止吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.99,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪的…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用木劍對真劍是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.63,0:04:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是拔刀齋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一定不會讓你逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心流  殺人的拔刀齋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心流是我們家的流派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙用我家的名字\N在街上亂殺人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好強的姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.58,0:05:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.58,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被拔刀齋打傷了…\N那之後怎麼了…啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是味曾湯的味道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行的  放這麼多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.35,0:06:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你起來了  真是可愛的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們相處的非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好…很好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.32,0:06:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在準備早飯\N所以先借一下院子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要一起吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…有這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不合你的口味嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我做的還好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.86,0:07:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處理的很快 傷口已經復合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.26,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是怎麼看也不像是劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很適合照顧小孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.97,0:07:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼這兩人\N不是小熏小姐的妹妹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對  她們是玄齋大夫的孫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.41,0:07:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經在這神谷道場\N當了三十年的主治醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.12,0:07:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿熏的父母死了後\N我就代替她父母照顧她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了  這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪漢先生如果不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在離開這城鎮之前\N你可以住在這道場裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我看你也不像有錢住旅店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是武士的悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你連小生的事也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.21,0:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到處流浪的人\N一定有什麼原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你問那麼多也沒用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐是這道場的師父嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心流\N是我父親所開創的流派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.37,0:08:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是傷人的而是讓人活的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.27,0:08:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活人劍是其理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.67,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那殺人魔竟冒充活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我父親的理想給弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會原諒他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,徒弟們好像來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧  雖然一個人不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集合神谷道場每個人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把那傢伙打倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位！你們都來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一定要把拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.40,0:08:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是來辭行的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.37,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被朋友在背後指指點點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說我是暗殺行人的神谷活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.87,0:09:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母親說會暗殺行人的道場\N絕對不能再去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼解釋也不相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒有信心再做下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.02,0:09:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是這道場所剩的最後三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使只有我一個人\N我也要守住道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…姐姐…好像在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行。。不行  不振作不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.01,0:10:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐！\N你怎麼了  小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.15,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以尋短見！不要自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我在這裏反省一個晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.10,0:10:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐  有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的門生有沒有一個左撇子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右手母指不能動的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那暗殺行人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.62,0:10:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說\N那傢伙是我們家的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.82,0:10:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心是以活人劍為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.39,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門下弟子應該不會殺人的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙是殺人拔刀齋吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿殺機的殺人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了父親的流派\N我即使喪失了生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要把那傢伙給打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以洗刷污名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.51,0:11:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你父親一定不希望小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捨棄自己的生命而保住流派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信你死去的父親所希望的一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪漢的你知道些什麼呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說得像知道了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.16,0:12:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死去的父親\N所希望的一定是小熏小姐的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~~真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.85,0:12:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…\N剛剛我好像說得太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經道歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒著吧！稍微回答一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問一下名字就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害。。只有一隻左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是伍兵衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊。。不是的是拔刀齋師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齋師傅\N今晚也要去殺人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時機到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼  就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我深刻體會到\N這母指不能動的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一點。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來。。哪一位想要流血的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏  退下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父！  神谷師父！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比留間\N為什麼不遵守我的訓誡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能傷人\N那是活心流的奧秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對你的教導\N已經感到厭煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍是殺人的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這刀有吸過血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你的血也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.59,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那手指已經不能再握劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經被逐出師門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.71,0:14:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准再進入這道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被切斷右手指的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.58,0:15:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了！十一年前被逐出師門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比留間…伍兵衛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然。。。。是你。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於想起來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.46,0:15:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這十一年裏我在地獄的深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.07,0:15:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祈禱著打敗神谷活心流的日子終於來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.97,0:15:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為報仇到處殺人\N以使我的名譽掃地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能有今天也要感謝你的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.75,0:15:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓他看看這十一年來\N所鍛煉左手的殺人劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.32,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父親。。父親的活心流\N才不會輸給你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點用處都沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.54,0:15:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺了你讓道場關閉後\N我的復仇也完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會慢慢的送你去地獄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再把地面剷平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.85,0:16:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？\N也讓你們用劍來吸血看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.62,0:16:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍是為了要救人而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有意思，哈。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.83,0:16:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈。。。。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那先救自己的命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼慢吞吞的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西力怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好。。厲。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪人？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把手放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你。。是。。昨天的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始我就應該把你打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不。。不行，你贏不了他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.44,0:16:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N你也認為劍是讓人活命的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍是兇器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍術是殺人術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐所說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.93,0:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從來沒有弄髒自己的手\N所說的笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.91,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，小生比較喜歡\N小熏小姐所說的玩笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.21,0:17:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在開始我想世界上\N的玩笑話都變成真實的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我上！把他折磨死也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.76,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退下！我不想讓受傷的人增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有人受傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有人會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你這傢伙一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.68,0:18:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一。。一個人\N一次讓4~5人  是妖術！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對！速度比別人快好幾倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道對手的動向後先下手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.13,0:18:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅色頭髮。。臉上十字的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.37,0:18:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘記說一件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人拔刀齋所揮的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是神谷活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.04,0:18:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是你流派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.62,0:18:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這把刀\N才有如此神速的殺人劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那。。你是。。真的。。殺人。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這世界上\N不需要有兩個拔刀齋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我才適合拔刀齋的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要把你打倒後\N最強的名字就是我的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得已。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧！拔刀齋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.46,0:19:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齋的名字沒有戀戀不捨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我不能把他\N讓給像你這樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.87,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想那手指\N真的不能再握劍了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.77,0:19:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不敢相信。。。大家都昏過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一個人是死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去報警把這男人所做的事\N告訴警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.48,0:19:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎？\N好。。。。好。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真對不起。。。。小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生並沒有打算瞞你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡可能不要說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，請保重。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣就要走了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.76,0:20:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我怎麼振作活心派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會幫我一下忙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說過\N我不會在乎別人的過去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是。。。好不容易都解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.94,0:20:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的拔刀齋還在這裏\N不是。。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.41,0:20:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有說要讓拔刀齋在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是希望流浪漢的你在。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你若堅持要走的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總要說出你的名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是傳說中殺人王的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是你的真名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,。。。緋村。。。緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。劍心  快滾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生已經有點累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.32,0:20:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知什麼時候\N會再流浪到哪裏喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不會煮菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明煮的比我還好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能誤闖進你的浴池裏。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係，那時侯我就。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.21,0:21:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨。。笨蛋！我以為你會躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.78,0:21:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大的力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.68,0:21:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖的！不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.49,0:21:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.00,0:21:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.86,0:21:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在神谷道場有一位新的居住者

